Shirene, this is the crux of the issue:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>This is because such activity sends the message to nonadherents that “they are outsiders, not full members of the political community.”<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
